<lb n="0770a21" ed="T"/><head type="no">No. 501</head>
<lb n="0770a22" ed="T"/><juan n="001" fun="open"><mulu n="001" type="卷"/><jhead>佛說沙曷比丘功德經</jhead></juan>
<lb n="0770a23" ed="T"/>
<lb n="0770a24" ed="T"/><byline type="Translator">西晉沙門<note n="0770012" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">（釋）＋法炬【三】【宮】</note><note n="0770012" resp="CBETA" type="mod">（釋）＋法炬【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0770012"><lem wit="【大】">法炬</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】">釋法炬</rdg></app>譯</byline>
<lb n="0770a25" ed="T"/><div1 type="jing"><p id="pT14p0770a2501">聞如是：</p><p id="pT14p0770a2504" place="inline">一時佛在舍衛國祇樹給孤獨園，時
<lb n="0770a26" ed="T"/>與千二百五十比丘、菩薩萬人。時須耶國有
<lb n="0770a27" ed="T"/>貧人，行賃剃小兒頭，所剃者皆約：「到麥熟，
<lb n="0770a28" ed="T"/>當各雇麥一斛。」適別未遠，道逢<note n="0770013" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">故＝雇【三】【宮】</note><note n="0770013" resp="CBETA" type="mod">故＝雇【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0770013"><lem wit="【大】">故</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】">雇</rdg></app>人，將其
<lb n="0770a29" ed="T"/>還。求麥，欲以取酒飲之。遍求，無以麥還者。於
<pb n="0770b" ed="T" id="T14.0501.0770b"/>
<lb n="0770b01" ed="T"/>是便起恚意言：「願我壽終後，作大神龍，當
<lb n="0770b02" ed="T"/>陷此國。」後壽終，魂神遂還作龍，其國中歷
<lb n="0770b03" ed="T"/>年風雨不時，五穀毀敗。</p><p id="pT14p0770b0310" place="inline">佛念此國人民飢饉，
<lb n="0770b04" ed="T"/>即遣沙曷比丘往化之。龍見比丘往，即興惡
<lb n="0770b05" ed="T"/>意，欲敗國及殺沙曷比丘。沙曷便變化&CB00425;，覆
<lb n="0770b06" ed="T"/>蓋一國。龍雨之，謂國已沒。比丘以佛威神，
<lb n="0770b07" ed="T"/>令龍見人民安隱如故。龍復興恚意下雪，比
<lb n="0770b08" ed="T"/>丘以&CB00425;受之。雪極，比丘以手掃之，著一處如
<lb n="0770b09" ed="T"/>山。比丘乃入龍室，龍即出，比丘復出；龍入，
<lb n="0770b10" ed="T"/>比丘復入。如是若干輩，龍極乃止，長跪問言：
<lb n="0770b11" ed="T"/>「卿何<note n="0770014" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">等神＝神等【元】【明】</note><app n="0770014"><lem wit="【大】">等神</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【元】【明】">神等</rdg></app>，惱我如此？」比丘言：「吾是佛弟子。」
<lb n="0770b12" ed="T"/>龍言：「我欲自歸於卿。」比丘答<note n="0770015" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔言〕－【聖】</note><app n="0770015"><lem wit="【大】">言</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【聖】">&lac;</rdg></app>：「吾有大師，
<lb n="0770b13" ed="T"/>佛三界最尊，卿當自歸之。」龍言：「佛在何所？」
<lb n="0770b14" ed="T"/>報言：「佛在舍衛國。」龍言：「乞逐道人去。」比丘
<lb n="0770b15" ed="T"/>言：「欲去者善！」便內龍著<note n="0770016" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">笥＝笱【三】【宮】</note><note n="0770016" resp="CBETA" type="mod">笥＝笱【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0770016"><lem wit="【大】">笥</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】">笱</rdg></app>中。</p><p id="pT14p0770b1512" place="inline">人民見比丘
<lb n="0770b16" ed="T"/>取龍如是，<note n="0770017" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">皆＝有【宮】</note><app n="0770017"><lem wit="【大】">皆</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宮】">有</rdg></app>歡喜問言：「道人是何等大神，
<lb n="0770b17" ed="T"/>降伏國患？」告言：「吾是佛弟子。」人民問言：「佛
<lb n="0770b18" ed="T"/>可得見不？」答言：「欲得見佛，且<note n="0770018" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">待＝須【三】【宮】【聖】</note><note n="0770018" resp="CBETA" type="mod">待＝須【宋】【元】【明】【宮】【聖】</note><app n="0770018"><lem wit="【大】">待</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】【聖】">須</rdg></app>吾<note n="0770019" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">還＝運【宮】</note><app n="0770019"><lem wit="【大】">還</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宮】">運</rdg></app>。」時
<lb n="0770b19" ed="T"/>日向中，道<note n="0770020" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">遇＝過【宮】</note><app n="0770020"><lem wit="【大】">遇</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宮】">過</rdg></app>分衛，人<note n="0770021" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔民〕－【聖】</note><app n="0770021"><lem wit="【大】">民</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【聖】">&lac;</rdg></app>或與飯者、與酒者，
<lb n="0770b20" ed="T"/>比丘受而食飲之，致酒醉，<note n="0770022" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">遇＝過【三】【宮】</note><note n="0770022" resp="CBETA" type="mod">遇＝過【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0770022"><lem wit="【大】">遇</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】">過</rdg></app>樹下臥，龍&CB00425;、袈
<lb n="0770b21" ed="T"/>裟各在一處。</p><p id="pT14p0770b2106" place="inline">佛<note n="0770023" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">時＝笑【宮】</note><app n="0770023"><lem wit="【大】">時</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宮】">笑</rdg></app>笑，五色光出，阿難<note n="0770024" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">正＝整【明】</note><app n="0770024"><lem wit="【大】">正</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【明】">整</rdg></app>
<lb n="0770b22" ed="T"/>衣服，叉手白佛言：「佛不妄笑，笑必有意！」佛
<lb n="0770b23" ed="T"/>告阿難：「汝為見沙曷比丘不？」阿難言：「不見。」佛
<lb n="0770b24" ed="T"/>言：「今在彼樹下醉臥。」</p><p id="pT14p0770b2409" place="inline">時千二百五十比丘、菩
<lb n="0770b25" ed="T"/>薩萬人，各相與語言：「沙曷比丘已得阿羅漢，
<lb n="0770b26" ed="T"/>何以復醉臥？」佛知諸人意有疑，因說四事：「一
<lb n="0770b27" ed="T"/>者，阿羅漢不三昧不得知；二者，不得便現神
<lb n="0770b28" ed="T"/>足；三者，不<note n="0770025" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">得＝張【三】【宮】【聖】</note><note n="0770025" resp="CBETA" type="mod">得＝張【宋】【元】【明】【宮】【聖】</note><app n="0770025"><lem wit="【大】">得</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】【聖】">張</rdg></app>強勸人分衛；四者，身中尚有
<lb n="0770b29" ed="T"/>蟲。阿羅漢以是四事不及佛。」時萬菩薩皆
<pb n="0770c" ed="T" id="T14.0501.0770c"/>
<lb n="0770c01" ed="T"/>迴意欲向羅漢。</p><p id="pT14p0770c0107" place="inline">佛遣目<note n="0770026" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">犍＝揵【聖】</note><app n="0770026"><lem wit="【大】">犍</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【聖】">揵</rdg></app>連往到沙曷比
<lb n="0770c02" ed="T"/>丘所，&CB00330;之攝龍來。龍以頭面為佛作禮，佛
<lb n="0770c03" ed="T"/>便為說宿<note n="0770027" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔命〕－【聖】</note><app n="0770027"><lem wit="【大】">命</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【聖】">&lac;</rdg></app>本末，龍心即解，受五戒，奉行
<lb n="0770c04" ed="T"/>十善，即得須陀洹道，為佛作禮而去。</p><p id="pT14p0770c0415" place="inline">佛時
<lb n="0770c05" ed="T"/>說沙曷比丘功德微妙。阿難叉手啟佛言：「沙
<lb n="0770c06" ed="T"/>曷比丘飲酒醉臥，而佛說其功德微妙乃爾？」</p>
<lb n="0770c07" ed="T"/><p id="pT14p0770c0701">佛告阿難：「阿羅漢不復飢渴，用三事故，現
<lb n="0770c08" ed="T"/>醉臥耳：一者，佛欲開化菩薩意；二者，不欲逆
<lb n="0770c09" ed="T"/>布施家意；三者，恐諸弟子未得道者，飲酒多
<lb n="0770c10" ed="T"/>失故。以此至戒撿之，沙曷比丘雖飲酒，是為
<lb n="0770c11" ed="T"/>不醉。」諸菩薩、四輩弟子，聞佛說是，皆起整
<lb n="0770c12" ed="T"/>衣服，為佛作禮。</p><p id="pT14p0770c1207" place="inline">沙曷比丘更前長跪白佛言：
<lb n="0770c13" ed="T"/>「須耶越國王、人民欲見。」<note n="0770028" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">（佛）＋佛【聖】</note><app n="0770028"><lem wit="【大】">佛</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【聖】">佛佛</rdg></app>默然受之。沙曷比
<lb n="0770c14" ed="T"/>丘即承佛教，如彈指頃，還到須耶越國。國
<lb n="0770c15" ed="T"/>王、人民見比丘，皆歡喜，有作禮者、有跪者、但
<lb n="0770c16" ed="T"/>叉手者。沙曷比丘告言：「佛明日當來到。」此
<lb n="0770c17" ed="T"/>王聞佛當來，大歡喜豫，於四衢道掃灑，廣施
<lb n="0770c18" ed="T"/>帳幔。</p><p id="pT14p0770c1803" place="inline">佛明日與千二百五十比丘俱，豫行空
<lb n="0770c19" ed="T"/>中，<note n="0770029" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔皆〕－【三】【宮】【聖】</note><note n="0770029" resp="CBETA" type="mod">〔皆〕－【宋】【元】【明】【宮】【聖】</note><app n="0770029"><lem wit="【大】">皆</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】【聖】">&lac;</rdg></app>有自然蓮華，<note n="0770030" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">奉＝捧【三】【宮】【聖】</note><note n="0770030" resp="CBETA" type="mod">奉＝捧【宋】【元】【明】【宮】【聖】</note><app n="0770030"><lem wit="【大】">奉</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】【聖】">捧</rdg></app>佛足下。王及<note n="0770031" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">臣＝人【明】</note><app n="0770031"><lem wit="【大】">臣</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【明】">人</rdg></app>民，
<lb n="0770c20" ed="T"/>皆以<note n="0770032" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">華香＝香華【三】【宮】</note><note n="0770032" resp="CBETA" type="mod">華香＝香華【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0770032"><lem wit="【大】">華香</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】">香華</rdg></app>，出城迎佛，五體投地，稽首為禮。
<lb n="0770c21" ed="T"/>佛及比丘到宮即有自然師子座，布以綩綖，
<lb n="0770c22" ed="T"/>七寶華蓋，五色交絡，<note n="0770033" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">王＝五【明】</note><app n="0770033"><lem wit="【大】">王</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【明】">五</rdg></app>施設供養，手自斟
<lb n="0770c23" ed="T"/>酌。飯畢，行<note n="0770034" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">&CB02900;＝盥【宋】</note><note n="0770034" resp="CBETA" type="mod">&CB02900;＝盥【宋】【麗-CB】【CB】</note><app n="0770034"><lem resp="CBETA.maha" cf1="K20n0851_p1197a14" wit="【CBETA】【麗】">盥</lem><rdg wit="【大】">&CB02900;</rdg><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】">盥</rdg></app>水，祝願。佛為王及人民說龍
<lb n="0770c24" ed="T"/>本末，王與人民心解，即受五戒，行十善，或
<lb n="0770c25" ed="T"/>得須陀洹者、斯陀含、阿那含、阿羅漢者，不
<lb n="0770c26" ed="T"/>可<note n="0770035" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">稱＝勝【三】【宮】</note><note n="0770035" resp="CBETA" type="mod">稱＝勝【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0770035"><lem wit="【大】">稱</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】">勝</rdg></app>數。</p><p id="pT14p0770c2604" place="inline">佛說經竟，四輩弟子、天龍鬼神，<note n="0770036" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">歡喜奉行＝皆歡喜作禮而去【三】【宮】【聖】</note><note n="0770036" resp="CBETA" type="mod">歡喜奉行＝皆歡喜作禮而去【宋】【元】【明】【宮】【聖】</note><app n="0770036"><lem wit="【大】">歡
<lb n="0770c27" ed="T"/>喜奉行</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】【聖】">皆歡喜作禮而去</rdg></app>。</p></div1>
<lb n="0770c28" ed="T"/><juan n="001" fun="close"><jhead><note n="0770037" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔佛說〕－【聖】</note><app n="0770037"><lem wit="【大】">佛說</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【聖】">&lac;</rdg></app>沙曷比丘功德經</jhead><note n="0770038" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">光明皇后願文【聖】</note></juan>
</body></text></TEI.2>